{"tid":755147,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【日本酷熱】官房長官：考慮延長暑假","createTime":"2018-07-25T03:31:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-25T08:04:19.000Z","uid":184679,"like":29,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"2d7a359dbe9027186883a152ed3ee2549bdcc8b6","tid":755147,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T03:31:05.000Z","msg":"日本高溫不斷，除了讓東京救護車出動次數破紀錄外，還導致京都花傘巡行停辦。不過，最值得注意的，還是有小學生，因學校沒有安裝冷氣，而中暑死亡的消息。對此，日本官房長官，在一場電視節目中，表示將考慮延長暑假。<br />\n<br />\n日本《NHK》報導，官房長官菅直人參加節目時，回顧近日該國酷熱天氣，已導致多人送醫急救，因此認爲必須加快在中小學購置冷氣，並考慮予以補貼。<br />\n<br />\n另外，菅直人還透露，日本政府將開始考慮，是否縮短寒假或延長暑假，來避免過熱天氣，導致相同悲劇再度發生。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://times.hinet.net/news/21875104\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftimes.hinet.net%2Fnews%2F21875104&d=URtt3CCGnuGnLRHpeOfLmv6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=6a0e11df\" target=\"_blank\">https://times.hinet.net/news/21875104</a>"},{"pid":"83c0f448ea9ded253b942071016261fb42d19042","tid":755147,"uid":41524,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T03:32:24.000Z","msg":"冇冷氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daace0cbcc6958c44aab71c74d628f1078bbf7c9","tid":755147,"uid":164913,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T03:34:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"915deafc3446b4607ec70987a8bb0224259dac0e","tid":755147,"uid":131323,"like":0,"dislike":22,"score":-22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T03:35:15.000Z","msg":"原來中小學會冇冷氣<br />\n唔知邊個連登仔話日本好住<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f6a76ccf92a8b0e0b41add60899be03328bd102","tid":755147,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T03:40:25.000Z","msg":"學下琦玉"},{"pid":"46bbb58db849338a986187056d92f23ae450c9e8","tid":755147,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T03:47:04.000Z","msg":"東亞病夫<br />\n<br />\n連冷氣都冇"},{"pid":"1d7d2326490aa66c5dbb56b2e8de7aad35b9d745","tid":755147,"uid